item.title: About me
item.author: contact@celiales.fr (Célia Alessandrini)
item.description: Hey you, how you doin'? Welcome. I am Celia Alessandrini. I am a 27 years old student. I’m about to start study programmation in october 2022 at the school ETNA. I don’t know how yet, but I will try to do some blogging content about my journey from noob to maybe front end developper. Or maybe video games developper. Or a cybersecurity profession… Hard to make a choice at the moment…!
